input_full.body:
Currently the orchestration model enforces a single `sbs-developer` agent at a time as an architectural invariant. The request is to relax this constraint specifically during the execution phase of `/task`, while keeping the single-agent constraint for all other phases (alignment, planning, finalization). This would allow parallelizing independent implementation subtasks within an approved plan.
